Reference(s): European Commission (2007) Integrated Pollution Prevention and Control, Reference Document on Best Available Techniques for the Production of Speciality Inorganic Chemicals, August 2007. Online http://eippcb.jrc.ec.europa.eu/reference/sic.html, accessed 29 June 2017</comment>
